wiki.summary: "I GUESS I'M IN LOVE" is a tender ballad that finds Clinton Kane falling properly in love for the first time. He details being truly smitten with his love interest; he adores the way his girlfriend helps him when he's depressed, how she loves the things he hates about himself, and even her little quirks, like an inability to sit still. Clinton Kane wrote this bare-bones ballad with his go-to producer Steve Rusch. Clinton Kane told Genius he wrote the song in 30 minutes while feeling passionate about a new relationship. wiki.content: "I GUESS I'M IN LOVE" is a tender ballad that finds Clinton Kane falling properly in love for the first time. He details being truly smitten with his love interest; he adores the way his girlfriend helps him when he's depressed, how she loves the things he hates about himself, and even her little quirks, like an inability to sit still. Clinton Kane wrote this bare-bones ballad with his go-to producer Steve Rusch. Clinton Kane told Genius he wrote the song in 30 minutes while feeling passionate about a new relationship. "hey family x i know i joke a lot ab being toxic, teasing songs constantly and blackmailing to the point where you feel like i’m dragging everything out and purposely taking so long to release songs just bc i want to, but honestly, some things are out of my control. i wanted to release this love song months ago but things kept coming up with videos and production for the song and im so sorry its taken so long for music to come out since ive teased it. i tried to make the best of the situation by teasing and joking around ab it. you are my family and i just wanted to let you know what was going on in the background. thank you for still being here and being patient w me. i love you so so much x i would be nothing without you guys x" - via Twitter “I GUESS I’M IN LOVE” debuted at #90 and peaked at #88 on the Billboard Hot 100 Chart during the week ending September 4, 2021.
